Message.SourceString: The statue has no further secrets for you.
Message.LocalizedString: The statue has no further secrets for you.

Message.SourceString: Still, I'm betting there's something interesting waiting around here. There are vaults in this place and they must be loaded with dragonkin secrets.
Message.LocalizedString: Still, I'm betting there's something interesting waiting around here. There are vaults in this place and they must be loaded with dragonkin secrets.

Message.SourceString: Taken a look in that locked vault yet? There must be a trick to it. Those dragonkin were a smart lot, secretive... and arrogant as heck.
Message.LocalizedString: Taken a look in that locked vault yet? There must be a trick to it. Those dragonkin were a smart lot, secretive... and arrogant as heck.

Message.SourceString: I don't like this place, it's creepy and weird. Had to whack several zombies with my hammer and now it's got this weird purple ooze on it that won't wash off.
Message.LocalizedString: I don't like this place, it's creepy and weird. Had to whack several zombies with my hammer and now it's got this weird purple ooze on it that won't wash off.

Message.SourceString: Oh, you don't appear to have the space for it. Come back and see me when you do.
Message.LocalizedString: Oh, you don't appear to have the space for it. Come back and see me when you do.

Message.SourceString: Well now, that is unexpected. This is the Salve amulet... why is this here? It requires a gemstone only found by the river Salve back in Misthalin. I mean, it's handy against the undead, so it'll be real useful here.
Message.LocalizedString: Well now, that is unexpected. This is the Salve amulet... why is this here? It requires a gemstone only found by the river Salve back in Misthalin. I mean, it's handy against the undead, so it'll be real useful here.

Message.SourceString: Oh! Ha, you're gonna laugh at this, but I actually have one of them river Salve gemstones. I found one a few years back and I just keep it with me as a good luck charm. Here, you should take it, make yourself one of those salve amulets.
Message.LocalizedString: Oh! Ha, you're gonna laugh at this, but I actually have one of them river Salve gemstones. I found one a few years back and I just keep it with me as a good luck charm. Here, you should take it, make yourself one of those salve amulets.

Message.SourceString: Who knows what you might find? I discovered one vault, and I was all geared up to visit, but it's locked down tight. Hey, I know, if you get a chance why don't you take a look? Let me know what you find inside.
Message.LocalizedString: Who knows what you might find? I discovered one vault, and I was all geared up to visit, but it's locked down tight. Hey, I know, if you get a chance why don't you take a look? Let me know what you find inside.

Message.SourceString: If you can find your way inside, let me know if you discover anything interesting.
Message.LocalizedString: If you can find your way inside, let me know if you discover anything interesting.

Message.SourceString: You hear the sound of a dragonkin lock releasing.
Message.LocalizedString: You hear the sound of a dragonkin lock releasing.

Message.SourceString: The door is sealed by Dragonkin magic.
Message.LocalizedString: The door is sealed by Dragonkin magic.

Message.SourceString: You find strange dwarven writings that you cannot read. Perhaps Doric can translate for you.
Message.LocalizedString: You find strange dwarven writings that you cannot read. Perhaps Doric can translate for you.

Message.SourceString: You find strange dwarven writings that you cannot read. Perhaps someone can translate for you.
Message.LocalizedString: You find strange dwarven writings that you cannot read. Perhaps someone can translate for you.

Message.SourceString: Well, will you look at that, another dwarven tablet. Why were the dragonkin out here stealing dwarven secrets?
Message.LocalizedString: Well, will you look at that, another dwarven tablet. Why were the dragonkin out here stealing dwarven secrets?

Message.SourceString: I guess we'll never know. Here, let me translate this for you, hopefully it'll help you on your travels.
Message.LocalizedString: I guess we'll never know. Here, let me translate this for you, hopefully it'll help you on your travels.
